#!/usr/local/projects/routing/help/html_filter.pl
<h2 align=center>Help for the <button>I</button> button</h2>
<button>I</button> asks the user for routes to include in this one.
Inclusion is done by adding the patrons on the included routes to this route.
<u><b>Important</b></u>:  The inclusion process does continue.  If you
subsequently add patrons to an included route, they will not appear in this
route without being included or having this route added to the routes for the
patron.

